<%- include("./include/_header") %>

    <title>실습점수계산기</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/tip.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/media.css">
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        body {
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        #calculatorForm {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        label, input {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        h1, h2, p {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>

    <p style="font-size: 20px;">3학년 외부실습 점수 계산</p>
    <p style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: bold;">점수 계산 방법</p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bolder;">(학점 + 상벌점/500) * 12.5 + 토익 점수 * 0.03 + 10</p>
    <p style="font-size: 10px; margin: 0;">*10점은 필수 과목 이수 여부 (F하나에 -1점)</p>
    <p style="font-size: 10px; margin: 0;">*상벌점 리미트 150점</p>

    <form id="calculatorForm">
        <label for="input1">학점:</label>
        <input type="number" id="input1" required>
        <br>
        <label for="input2">상벌점:</label>
        <input type="number" id="input2" required>
        <br>
        <label for="input3">토익:</label>
        <input type="number" id="input3" required>
    </form>
    <h2>점수</h2>
    <p id="result"></p>

    <script src="/js/calc.js"></script>

<%- include("./include/_footer") %>